      "column": "left",
      "text": "Runna us teem\nIsraeta Behrneem/ un fakki us\nteem: Kad juhs tai Semmē juj-\nfas Mischanas nahkfeet / ko es\njuins dohfchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un juhs tam KUNGAM\ngribbat weenu Ugguni pataisfht/\nweenu Dedsamu-Uppuri/ jeb Up-\npuri sawadas Apfohlifchanas\npehz / jeb kahdu Uppuri no labba\nPrahta / jeb juhfs nosazzitōs\nSwehtēds/darridami tam KUN-\nGAM weenu faldn Smarfchn/\nno leeieim jeb sihkeem Lohpeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad buhs tam / kas farwu\nUppuri tam KUNGAM peeneffs/\nweenu Ehdamu-Uppuri / no wee-\nnas definitas Teefas Kweeschu-\nMiltu / kas ar weenu Zettortni\nno weena Inna Efjesfajaukts irr/\nuppureht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un par Dserramu-Uppuri/\nweenu Zettortni no weena Inna\nWihna / buhs tew fataifiht par\nweenu Dedsamu-Uppuri/ jeb par\nUppuri / fur weens Jehrs uppu-\nrehts tohp.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jeb kad weens Auns up-\npurehts tohp / buhs tew weenu\nEhdanu-Uppuri fataifiht no di-\nwi Kweeschu-Miltu Definiteem/\nkas fajaukti ar to treschu Teefu\nno weena Inna Efjes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Wihnu par Dserramu-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ja tu weenu jaunu\nWehrti gribbi fataifiht par De-\ndsamu-Uppuri/jeb Uppuri kahdas\nsawadas Apfohlifchanas deht /\njeb par Pateifschanas - Uppuri\ntam KUNGAM.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad buhs winnam pee ta\njauna Wehrfcha weenu Ehdamu-\nUppuri peelift / trihs Kweeschu-\nMiltu Definitus / fajauktus ar\nweenu puhs Innu Efjes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Wihnu buhs tew up-\npureht par Dserramu-Uppuri/\nweenu puhs Innu par Ugguni/\nweenu faldn Smarschu tam\nKUNGAM.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta laid tas darrihts tohp\nar weenu Wehrft / jeb ar weenu\nAunn / jeb ar tihku Lohpu / ne\nJehreem/jeb no Kasahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz to Pulku / ko juh-\nfataifiht / buhs jums ta darrih-\nar ikweenu pehz farwu Pulku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiffam / kas pee jum-\ndsinmis irr / buhs schahs Leeta\nta darriht / uppuredams ween-\nUgguni par faldn Smarschu tam\nKUNGAM.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja arridsan weens Swe-\nschinecks pee jums par Swesch-\nneeku miht/ jeb juhsu Starpā po-\njuhsu Raddeen irr / un grib tam\nKUNGAM par faldn Smarfch-\nweenu Ugguni taijht / tam buh-\nta darriht/ ittin ka juhs darrat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiffai Draudsei laid i-\nwe\n"
